{"tid":2383233,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[ling嘢長文] 嫌自己個名太普通，想霸氣啲","createTime":"2021-01-27T19:03:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T22:36:59.000Z","uid":302951,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9121908f2bfd6a32a267ea998af15b0fbc700e3e","tid":2383233,"uid":302951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T19:03:16.000Z","msg":"建議睇咗上一篇先<br />\n[ling嘢長文] 其實埃及象形字幾似中文<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2381250\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2381250</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：樓豬樓豬，我嫌腦魔Lomore太普通，想要個霸氣啲嘅名，你有咩建議？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：埃及象形文字──聖書體夠唔夠霸氣？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：夠啊！點寫㗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：簡單嚟講，我地參考下圖，用表音符號盡量還原你個名嘅讀音。有啲似將Mary譯做瑪莉咁。幅圖涵括大部分單音符號，應該夠大家用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BZHHwaQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBZHHwaQ.png&h=27c41f37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qpCsHhM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqpCsHhM.png&h=1dc47057&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺開始之前，有幾樣嘢要注意：<br />\n<br />\n1/ 埃及文字唔標母音aeiou，有必要時會用近似嘅滑音w y、或喉音A a代替。<br />\n<br />\n2/ 埃及文字有啲欠缺嘅音，例如l v c等等，要用近似音代替。<br />\n<br />\n3/ 紅色嘅符號係後期先出現嘅寫法，你可以跟據個人喜好，選擇採用舊式或者新式。<br />\n<br />\n4/ 一個名可以有幾種譯法，就好似Mary可以係瑪莉、瑪利、瑪麗、馬莉、馬利、馬麗。<br />\n<br />\n5/聖書體係一種好着重美感嘅文字，如果你個名夠長，有好多符號時，可以喺唔影響閱讀順序嘅情況下，疊起啲符號。<br />\n<br />\n6/ 呢篇剩係教音譯，意譯因為樓豬修行未夠高，教唔到大家。唔巧意思！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：好，入正題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：Lomore可以拆做lo-more兩個音節，轉寫做n-m-A，分別係波浪、新 &bull; 貓頭鷹、同禿鷹。喺最尾加返個男仔符號，表示呢抽係人名。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7by7Hm8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7by7Hm8.png&h=464cb132&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我叫Minnie，個名又會係點？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：m-n-Y，貓頭鷹、波浪、新 &bull; 蘆葦，加女仔符號<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v5VRpAC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv5VRpAC.png&h=4bfed6d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：咁我呢？我叫Minmin啊！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：呢個情況特別啲，你當然可以用四個單音m-n-m-n，但係亦可以用兩個雙音mn-mn，睇落短啲。最後加返神嘅符號。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5VyWAHq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5VyWAHq.png&h=329751fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：就係咁啦！大家可以試下砌自己個名，如果唔識砌，可以喺下面問。如果你個名好特別嘅，唔好自爆。"},{"pid":"5d31fb2381a5080eb00743aed74519fbdba9e3e8","tid":2383233,"uid":134103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T19:16:15.000Z","msg":"有啲複雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過好多謝你咁有心整合哂，又舉咗幾個例子幫手理解，推廣學術風氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n已經正評咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />順手幫你推埋Po<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cffdc4c619f1eb759297a5dd5c3ef028ed2e73a6","tid":2383233,"uid":302951,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d31fb2381a5080eb00743aed74519fbdba9e3e8","tid":2383233,"uid":134103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T19:16:15.000Z","msg":"有啲複雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過好多謝你咁有心整合哂，又舉咗幾個例子幫手理解，推廣學術風氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n已經正評咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />順手幫你推埋Po<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T19:35:55.000Z","msg":"多謝ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我試下呢度打清楚啲步驟，希望多啲人睇得明<br />\n<br />\n1/ 抽取子音（aeiou以外嘅音）<br />\n例：A<span class=\"red\">l</span>e<span class=\"red\">x</span> &gt;&gt;&gt; l x<br />\n<br />\n2/ 檢查有無埃及文字缺少嘅音，有就用近音代替<br />\n例：l <span class=\"red\">x</span> &gt;&gt;&gt; l k s<br />\n<br />\n3/ 補返啲無咗唔得嘅母音<br />\n例：l k s &gt;&gt;&gt; <span class=\"red\">A</span> l k s<br />\n（可以無咗 e，但係 a 要保留，咪係就變Lex）<br />\n<br />\n4/ 換做象形文字，完成！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例：A l k s &gt;&gt;&gt; 禿鷹 獅子 籃 門閂"},{"pid":"0fbdc273897724c55ceae72c8b4a6e0427b1526b","tid":2383233,"uid":134103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cffdc4c619f1eb759297a5dd5c3ef028ed2e73a6","tid":2383233,"uid":302951,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d31fb2381a5080eb00743aed74519fbdba9e3e8","tid":2383233,"uid":134103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T19:16:15.000Z","msg":"有啲複雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過好多謝你咁有心整合哂，又舉咗幾個例子幫手理解，推廣學術風氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n已經正評咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />順手幫你推埋Po<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T19:35:55.000Z","msg":"多謝ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我試下呢度打